| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-2868 — Recovery Inhibition (darkvault)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 3fb9cc6d-cd5b-5f42-8c33-f7424f79c223"
